function evaluateProperty({
    api,
    helpers
}) {
    var records = api.data.get_all_accounts.results;
    if (records === undefined)
        return;
    const accounts = [];
    records.forEach(record => accounts.push({
        id: record._row_data.uniqueValue,
        label: record._row_data.displayValue
    }));
    return accounts;
